{"tid":1974482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約唔撚聽Wuhan Hygiene Office，要求所有人外出用罩","createTime":"2020-04-16T01:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T01:14:49.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"275842e51218e7b0760b8f5d5c8c1752576cd358","tid":1974482,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T01:14:12.000Z","msg":"紐約州長科莫周三（15日）宣布簽署行政命令，於無法保持社交距離情況下，所有人須在公眾地方佩戴口罩或掩蓋鼻、口；措施有3天寬限期，初期對不遵從者暫不予處罰，惟若執行情況不佳，將實行民事處罰。<br />\n<br />\n科莫表示，當地周二（14日）有752人因新型冠狀病毒肺炎死亡，較前一日輕微下跌，認為疫情已趨平穩。紐約州確診病例逾20萬宗，約佔全國三分之一，超過1.15萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n根據約翰霍普金斯大學數據，截至本港時間周四（16日）早上8時，美國累計逾63.6萬宗確診病例，累計超過2.8萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200416/s00005/1586996285781/%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e5%b7%9e%e4%b8%8b%e4%bb%a4%e5%a4%96%e5%87%ba%e6%88%b4%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200416%2Fs00005%2F1586996285781%2F%25e7%25b4%2590%25e7%25b4%2584%25e5%25b7%259e%25e4%25b8%258b%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2587%25ba%25e6%2588%25b4%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=35309f3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200416%2Fs00005%2F1586996285781%2F%25e7%25b4%2590%25e7%25b4%2584%25e5%25b7%259e%25e4%25b8%258b%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2587%25ba%25e6%2588%25b4%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9&h=38173a46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200416/s00005/1586996285781/%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e5%b7%9e%e4%b8%8b%e4%bb%a4%e5%a4%96%e5%87%ba%e6%88%b4%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9</a>"},{"pid":"ff21ef5b42257bff2ad261bf645fdf00e104270f","tid":1974482,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T01:14:49.000Z","msg":"坡狗都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 